{"type": "article", "id": 28080, "title": "翻转背包", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-13T07:00:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171722XqAL5DxIWTj8cB2r.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>传统的包袋设计往往针对的是比较单一的需求，根据场合还要搭配不同的背包，台湾创意团队 Allrover 最近就推出了一款跨越各种限制的翻转背包 FlipBag，可以在弹指间由背包变成手提袋、邮差包甚至是行李袋。背包采用 100% 涤纶和 PVC 胶制成，不仅防水还有高耐磨和抗尘性。FlipBag 的左右两边有着独立的收纳系统，转换时也不用担心物件会掉出。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/flipbag\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 3780 新台币。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171720asjuFWbU9xCwnh0N.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171720JuwEyb0UeqnYKHQp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43884892\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171721JhrmOvSd3qCbIAM1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171721wdx3VPXTA9B7Qmtb.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66627907\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}